<item>
            <title>[PIG-4973] Bigdecimal divison fails</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-4973</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Division of BigDecimals doesn&apos;t work because we&apos;re not passing scale and rounding information in divide() method. In cases like 10/3 we&apos;ll get ArithmeticException:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Pig script:&lt;br/&gt;
grunt&amp;gt; A = LOAD &apos;decimaltest/f1&apos; USING PigStorage(&apos;,&apos;) AS (id,col1:bigdecimal,col2:bigdecimal);&lt;br/&gt;
grunt&amp;gt; B = foreach A generate col1, col2, col1/col2;&lt;br/&gt;
grunt&amp;gt; dump B&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Input file content:&lt;br/&gt;
1,10.0,3&lt;br/&gt;
2,51651351.13153143512,10.00&lt;br/&gt;
3,252525.252525,123.456&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Output with bigdecimal type in the schema:&lt;/p&gt;

